---
model: googleai/gemini-2.5-flash
config:
  temperature: 0.1
input:
  schema:
    title: string
    content: string
output:
  format: json
  schema:
    category: string, one of: architecture, database, frontend, backend, devops, security, performance, testing, ai-tooling
    severity: string, one of: low, medium, high, critical
    tags(array): string, relevant search and topic tags
    summary: string, 1-2 sentences summarizing the content
---
Analyze the following document and classify it. Return a JSON object matching the requested schema.

Title: {{title}}
Content:
{{content}}
